    <item>
      <title>维京游轮公司股价在美国首次公开募股后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/cruise-line-viking-s-shares-rise-after-us-ipo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在扩大首次公开募股筹集 15.4 亿美元后，这家豪华游轮运营商的股价在首个交易日上涨了 12%，这表明美国上市复苏的范围仍在扩大。彭博社的阿比盖尔·杜立特还有更多。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/cruise-line-viking-s-shares-rise-after-us-ipo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 17:52:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大铁路工人投票罢工，威胁供应链</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/workers-gear-up-for-strike-against-two-canada-rail-giants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[要求更多休息时间的铁路工人接近罢工，罢工将扰乱从哈利法克斯到温哥华、中西部到墨西哥湾的供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/workers-gear-up-for-strike-against-two-canada-rail-giants</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 17:41:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
